Package com.controller

Class MenuItemController

java.lang.Object
com.controller.MenuItemController
All Implemented Interfaces:
CreatorController<MenuItem>
public class MenuItemController extends Object implements CreatorController<MenuItem>
MenuItemController.java A controller class that realises the CreatorController interface. It consists of methods that will enable its users to control the outcome of a MenuItem object.
